\section{Three-Loop Positivity Sectors} 
\label{sec:3loopsectors}


We shall now study the positivity sectors of $G_+ (0,4;1)^3$ in detail. In this section we will present the stratification of all 8 sectors. In {\S\ref{{sec:assembling}}} we shall turn our attention to the process of gluing sectors together.


\subsection{The $\{+,+,+\}$ Sector} 
\label{sec:+++}


Let us begin by reviewing the stratification of $G_+ (0,4;3)$, already presented in \cite{Franco:2014csa}. As described in {\S\ref{{sec:amplboundaries}}} and discussed in detail in \cite{Franco:2014csa}, we shall begin by constructing the $\Gamma_0$ boundaries and in each element in $\Gamma_0$  find the appropriate $\Gamma_1$ boundaries.


\paragraph{$\boldsymbol{\Gamma_0}$ Boundaries.}

